Text: Thank you for registering with Cheap TicketsPLEASE SAVE THIS EMAIL FOR YOUR RECORDS Dear Susan Welcome to Cheap Tickets Youve selected the best site on the Internet to find discount air tickets With more than nonpublished discount airfares we offer fares you sometimes cant find anywhere else The search is easy and free Simply point your browser to to get started You can search for fares right from the home page using Express Search Its only one click to view a list of available itineraries Or try the Power Search to see a list of discount fares One more click shows available itineraries SERVICES Whether youre just looking for low fares or youre ready to make a reservation or purchase tickets Cheap Tickets lets you be the travel agent Theres no charge and no obligation to search our extensive database of low airfares And when youre ready its only five clicks to purchase a ticket Need a hotel room for your next vacation We have rooms available at up to off published rates and many times can find you a room for sold out dates Visit us at hotels to save money on your hotel reservations If you like our airfares youll love our cruise rates For details on booking your next cruise at big savings with Cheap Tickets check us out at cruises PRIVACY AND SECURITY At Cheap Tickets were committed to making the process of travel planning and purchasing easy and safe for you Cheap Tickets assures your right to privacy We wont share your personal information with others without your consent And our No Worry Security means your purchases are safe with Cheap Tickets We use encryption technology to make sure private information stays private CUSTOMER SUPPORT Need help Once you login the Internets best help system is a click away A context sensitive popup Help link is available on every page of the fare search When in doubt you can view all help information by going to help Its simple and free Answers to frequently asked questions are also available at faq Buying discount tickets is easy but occasionally problems do arise If you cant find an answer to your question using one of the Help links above you can receive Customer Support at support Thank you for registering with Cheap Tickets We know youll find the site easy to use We look forward to saving you money with our discount airfares hotels and cruises Thanks again Cheap Tickets support help faq Traded on NASDAQ as CTIX

Thank you for registering with Cheap TicketsTHIS EMAIL FOR YOUR RECORDS Dear craig Congratulations on becoming a Cheap Tickets registered member Youve just taken the first step to making the most of your travel budget Your login name is CDEAN We suggest you save this email as a reminder Youll need your login name and password to use some of the services on our site Remember your login name and password are sensitive information Please protect them to prevent unauthorized use of your account DISCOUNT AIRFARE Choose from over million discount fares on major airlines The search is easy and free just visit Only four clicks to purchase an airline ticket and youre on your way HOTELS RENTAL CARS AND CRUISES TOO Find brandname hotel rooms up to off published rates at hotels Get exceptional savings on rental cars at cars Explore discount cruises to almost every destination in paradise at cruises PRIVACY AND SECURITY Were committed to making your travel planning and purchasing safe Cheap Tickets assures your privacy Review our our privacy statement at aboutusprivacyhtml CUSTOMER SUPPORT Help is just a click away help Find answers to frequently asked questions and assistance with making reservations Thank you for making Cheap Tickets your premier travel provider We look forward to serving you Sincerely Cheap Tickets IncR
